{"tid":1491410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現新疫症 - 社交媒體潔癖症","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T12:24:11.000Z","uid":73959,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d5bf9a8411d9ba511c1d439496be7ae3e2bc8f46","tid":1491410,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大家身邊有冇一啲朋友<br />\n非常活躍於社交媒體<br />\n但由69開始到而家從來冇喺social media上表過態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依然吃喝玩樂post去旅行相<br />\n<strong>連黑相/bless hk/文宣相都冇post過</strong><br />\n佢哋未必一定係政治冷感<br />\n只係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔想污染自己一直建立嘅形象</span></span></strong><br />\n呢啲簡稱社交媒體潔癖症<br />\n<br />\n如果你話你係明星 or 公眾人物 or KOL<br />\n如果你話你身邊有好多藍絲<br />\n都叫可以理解你點解沉默<br />\n<br />\n但係嗰種得幾百/幾千人follow<br />\n又唔係咩公眾人物<br />\n係呢啲情況下仲可以<br />\n好有心機維護自己social media形象嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係好撚嘔心呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申我唔係要所有人表態<br />\n因為實有啲眾人皆醉最我獨醒嘅人會屌返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話咩岀咗聲都唔代表有咩幫助<br />\n唔通出去發夢又要po岀嚟咩etc.<br />\n<br />\n講得岀呢啲嘅唔該縮返去你老母個閪度啦<br />\n你有冇出大家心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返返正題<br />\n我係針對嗰種到呢一刻仲好活躍social media<br />\n未必係政治冷感<br />\n只係純粹保持住靚靚profile而唔出聲嘅嗰班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋真係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好可悲</span></span><br />\n鬧都唔敢鬧<br />\n為咗嘅就係保持自己喺social media建立嘅形象 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家身邊有冇呢啲人<br />\n歡迎cap佢哋睇<br />\n提下佢哋係時候要睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f312f968efa27330d56435646bd363b0fc0a79f4","tid":1491410,"uid":156326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"可能佢地係藍。。"},{"pid":"5f1c6bf3785c94d5fb543b56250c1469dd17c8d9","tid":1491410,"uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f312f968efa27330d56435646bd363b0fc0a79f4","tid":1491410,"uid":156326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"可能佢地係藍。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:01:57.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n身邊真係有好幾個想保持男神女神形象<br />\n但其實又唔知自己好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b9b012ead48f7bbf6a165ba847b2e2ebb2de64","tid":1491410,"uid":287462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"認真 ig po個story都好"},{"pid":"cf0c6c5caa8917ca19ecccbc18bc818ce7667e29","tid":1491410,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"算吧啦，呢D人遲早比人批，為social而social。<br />\n由而家開始要po黑警醜態gif圖集合錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQzi0Ph.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQzi0Ph.gif&h=87b54f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n晚晚用黎po下twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXqqFPq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXqqFPq.gif&h=7c07ce48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洗下狗招post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0SP7uJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0SP7uJ.gif&h=945a9932&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n覺得好既幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1483792/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1483792/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfwQRWD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2